elementor-element-3fb9b3c elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"3fb9b3c\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-cc88e83\" data-id=\"cc88e83\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fa06ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8fa06ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Inflammatory Breast Cancer<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-a47a8d9 elementor-section-stretched elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"a47a8d9\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;stretch_section&quot;:&quot;section-stretched&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-ef5062f\" data-id=\"ef5062f\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-960cddb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"960cddb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Basics<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Very Aggressive Locally Advanced Breast Cancer<\/li><li>Highly Angiogenic &amp; Angioinvasive (High Metastatic Potential)<\/li><li><strong>Almost All Have Lymph Node Involvement<\/strong><\/li><li>Almost 1\/3 Have Distant Metastases<\/li><li>Automatically T4 Staging<\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Types<\/strong><\/p><ul><li><em>Primary Inflammatory Breast Cancer<\/em>: De Novo Inflammatory Breast Cancer<\/li><li><em>Secondary Inflammatory Breast Cancer<\/em>: An Inflammatory Recurrence of a Noninflammatory Primary Breast Cancer<ul><li>Often Occurs on the Chest Wall at the Site of Prior Mastectomy<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Presentation<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Breast Pain<\/li><li>Rapidly Growing Mass (Weeks-Months)<\/li><li>Warmth<\/li><li>Erythema &amp; Edema<\/li><li>\u201cPeau d\u2019Orange\u201d: Lymphedema from <strong>Dermal Lymphatic Invasion<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Diagnosis<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Initial Evaluation: Physical Exam, Imaging &amp; Biopsies<\/li><li>Biopsies:<ul><li>Core Needle Biopsy \u2013 To Establish Invasive Carcinoma<\/li><li><strong>Full Thickness Punch Biopsy of Skin<\/strong> (Usually \u2265 2 Biopsies) \u2013 To Establish Dermal Lymphatic Invasion<\/li><li>US-Guided FNA of Suspicious Lymph Nodes<\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>Diagnostic Criteria:<ul><li>Rapid Onset of Erythema, Edema, Warmth and\/or Peau d\u2019Orange<\/li><li>Duration \u2264 6 Months<\/li><li>Erythema Occupying \u2265 1\/3 the Breast<\/li><li>Pathologic Confirmation of Invasive Carcinoma<\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><p><strong>Treatment<\/strong><\/p><ul><li>Primary Treatment:<ul><li><strong>Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Modified Radial Mastectomy (MRM)<\/strong><\/li><li><strong>Adjuvant<\/strong> <strong>Radiation Therapy<\/strong><\/li><\/ul><\/li><li>If Tumor Remains Inoperable with Minimal Response After Multiple Rounds of Neoadjuvant Chemotherapy: Avoid Surgery &amp; Treat with Radiation Therapy Alone<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-8179b5f\" data-id=\"8179b5f\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1efec01 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1efec01\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor-clearfix\">\n\t\t\t\t<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-13559 \" src=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Inflammatory-Breast-Cancer-Right.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"276\" srcset=\"https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Inflammatory-Breast-Cancer-Right.jpg 500w, https:\/\/operativereview.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/10\/Inflammatory-Breast-Cancer-Right-300x166.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/><\/p><p>Inflammatory Breast Cancer <sup>1<\/sup><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-36d8b2c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"36d8b2c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-text-editor elementor